{"tid":1978483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢個咩世界嚟，WHO總幹事原來係恐怖分子嚟","createTime":"2020-04-18T17:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T13:35:24.000Z","uid":211994,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61255c8283c737af8d24c19976260e38d64b0aaa","tid":1978483,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"首先呢篇報道話<span style=\"color: gold;\">譚德塞以前加入嘅組織係恐怖組織嚟：</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3135105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3135105&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=43a31ea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3135105&h=de114122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3135105</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣大學政治學系名譽教授明居正14日爆出，WHO秘書長譚德塞（見圖）具有共產黨背景，是衣索比亞「提格雷人民解放陣線」的重要成員，港媒也報導指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">該政黨在90年代曾被美國政府列為恐怖組織。</span><br />\n<br />\n然後呢篇報道指譚德塞係該組織<span style=\"color: gold;\">權力最大的三位領袖之一：</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/15/road-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Froad-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=ea65dc4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/15/road-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano/</a><br />\n（最尾個一段）<br />\n<br />\n2018 年，當地媒體 Kichuu News 批評譚德塞不理數以百萬計受迫害的奧羅莫人生死，指他不配總幹事之位。美國「霍士新聞」引述埃塞俄比亞當地記者指，譚德塞是提人陣權力最大的三位領袖之一，<span style=\"color: red;\">他絕對要為政府的謀殺、酷刑、濫捕、搶地等暴行負上責任。</span><br />\n<br />\n英文版報道，尾二個段<br />\n<br />\n即係標題<span style=\"color: gold;\">&ldquo;MOZAMBIQUE CHOLERA CASES JUMP TO 139 A DAY AFTER OUTBREAK&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/world/who-chief-tedros-questionable-past-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fwho-chief-tedros-questionable-past-coronavirus&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=d49b8ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fwho-chief-tedros-questionable-past-coronavirus&h=a363dfdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/world/who-chief-tedros-questionable-past-coronavirus</a><br />\n<br />\n關於呢一個組織嘅描述：<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tigray_People's_Liberation_Fron\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTigray_People%27s_Liberation_Fron&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=fc6b7ced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tigray_People's_Liberation_Fron</a>"},{"pid":"183ec4a7e919f51d366d024d137377fd685051b4","tid":1978483,"uid":245065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ce39262beebac3077f2335c2cd4310a247c12ea","tid":1978483,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"而家都搞死左十幾萬人啦，勁過拉登N倍"},{"pid":"e34615b7651221d043cf85899c6c741cf467bf97","tid":1978483,"uid":148473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183ec4a7e919f51d366d024d137377fd685051b4","tid":1978483,"uid":245065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:59:55.000Z","msg":"hi 五毛"},{"pid":"6b5c2086de30f8bccd8055f0074bcc0bd976a523","tid":1978483,"uid":148473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WW4VW6J-5S0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWW4VW6J-5S0&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=a29af9c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WW4VW6J-5S0</a>"},{"pid":"a68d2e26425b5b9da96158c7ad0d5a13a9a6aad8","tid":1978483,"uid":14847